Key Match Events: Abdoulaye Seck scored the only goal for Senegal
Iliman Ndiaye scored a late goal to secure Senegal's victory
Post-Match Reflections: Senegal maintained their 100% record in defense of their AFCON title
Guinea finished third in Group C and will advance with four points as one of the four best third-place group finishers
Miscellaneous Highlights: Cameroon won their match against The Gambia to secure their spot in the last 16
Others: The match was a derby clash between west African neighbors
Guinea looked set to face Equatorial Guinea in the next round, while Senegal will meet a third-place team from Group A or F
